        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Profitability Trends:</strong> While early-stage growth companies may operate at a loss, we look for a clear path to profitability or expanding operating margins for established players.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Valuation Context:</strong> Growth is valuable, but price matters. We analyze Forward P/E and Price-to-Sales ratios relative to historical averages and industry peers to avoid overpaying.</li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;"><strong>Balance Sheet Strength:</strong> A strong cash position and manageable debt levels provide the financial flexibility necessary to fund future growth initiatives and weather economic downturns.</li>
